  "title": "Luxury Retail Sales Associate | $3,000 - $3,800 + Comm",
  "description": "<p>🌟 <strong>Luxury Retail Sales Associate | $3,000 - $3,800 + Comms</strong>🌟<br /><em>📍 Orchard, MBS</em></p><p>Are you passionate about luxury, fashion, and delivering exceptional customer experiences? Join a renowned luxury brand and be part of an elegant, high-performing retail team.</p><p><br />✨ <strong>Your Role</strong></p><ul><li><p>Deliver personalised, high-touch service to local and international clientele</p></li><li><p>Build strong client relationships and develop a loyal customer base</p></li><li><p>Achieve individual and store sales targets with confidence and professionalism</p></li><li><p>Maintain impeccable store presentation and visual merchandising standards</p></li><li><p>Handle sales transactions and after-sales service with accuracy and care</p></li></ul><p><br />💎 <strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prior experience in luxury retail, premium fashion, jewellery, or high-end hospitality</p></li><li><p>Well-groomed, confident, and customer-centric personality</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Sales-driven mindset with a passion for luxury brands</p></li><li><p>Able to work retail hours, including weekends and public holidays</p></li></ul><p><br /><br /><strong>📩 Apply Now</strong></p><p>Submit your resume to</p><p>📧 Email : <a href=\"mailto:annabelle.koh@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">annabelle.koh@crew.sg</a></p><p>📱 WhatsApp : <a href=\"tel:80882564\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">80882564</a><br /> </p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /> </p><p><strong>Annabelle Koh (R25158748)</strong></p><p><strong>Hrnet Ventures Pte Ltd - Crew by Hrnet</strong></p><p><strong>E.A.24C2435</strong></p>",
